Q.iframe_uploader - small library for JavaScript to upload file on a remote server without refresh page.

Example:

	<form action="/urlto/test.php" method="post" onsubmit="Q.iframe_uploader.submit(this, callback);">
		<input type="text" name="test" />
		<input type="submit" />
	</form>

	<script type="text/javascript">
		var callback = function(d) {
			alert(d);
		}
	</script>